data.description: Investors, seize the opportunity! This fully-equipped property, presents a lucrative rental income potential. Currently yielding excellent returns, the home accommodates multiple tenants, ensuring a favorable rental outcome for homeowners. Situated in the heart of Naples, Florida, this coastal-style beach cottage is just minutes away from downtown Naples' 5th Avenue and the pristine white sandy beaches. The property boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, featuring a separate guest quarters for additional occupants. The open-concept floor plan is adorned with tile floors, granite countertops, and recent upgrades, including a new roof. Given the robust demand for vacation rentals in Naples, whether for seasonal or year-round stays, this property promises outstanding potential for investors seeking robust returns. Act promptly, as this remarkable opportunity is not likely to endure!
